# Assets Balancing Item Household Loans Advances Impairment Amount

## identifier
de7815

## type
float

## definition
This is a balancing item in the list in which it is being used.

This is the value of revisions for impairment in relation to Loans and Advances being financial assets as determined in accordance with accounting standards, other than:
- Trade Receivables;
- Cash;
- Revolving Credit;
- Credit Cards;
- Loans for Housing; and
- Lease financing

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Assets.BalancingItemHouseholdLoansAdvancesImpairment.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
